title: Local Hour: The Dolphins Pie Chart
description:
After the Dolphins win yet again, we determine who deserves the most credit via our "Miami Dolphins Pie Chart" and then assess how Witty feels about Tua...Is he good? Is he great? Then, Klay Thompson and Russell Wilson's actions from over the weekend lead us to a conversation about authenticity from athletes.
